  <img border="0" height="221" src="../../signjpegs/s/sonb3.jpg" width="258"/>
  <img border="0" height="221" src="../../signjpegs/s/sonb4.jpg" width="258"/>
 </p>
 <font face="Arial">
  <hr align="left" color="#000000" size="1"/>
 </font>
 <p>
 </p>
 <p>
  SON: VERSION 2:
  <br/>
  In this version you can see the "MALE" + "BABY" parts of the sign.
  <br/>
  But remember -- DON'T rock your arms when signing SON or DAUGHTER!   
They are compound signs and use reduced movement.
 </p>
